# ğŸ—“ï¸ Multi-Agent Event Planner

An AI-powered **Multi-Agent Event Planner** built with [CrewAI](https://github.com/joaomdmoura/crewai) and [Streamlit](https://streamlit.io/). This app demonstrates how multiple AI agents can collaborate to plan, organize, and review events efficiently.

