## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation & Setup

1. Clone the repository  

    git clone https://github.com/saadtoorx/multi-agent-event-planner.git  
    cd multi-agent-event-planner  

2. Install dependencies  

    pip install -r requirements.txt  

3. Configure environment variables by creating a `.env` file:  

    OPENAI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here  

---

## â–¶ï¸ Running the App

    streamlit run app.py

- ğŸ“ Input your event details (e.g., "Corporate Tech Conference 2025").  
- ğŸ§  Agents collaborate on venue, logistics, and marketing tasks.  
- ğŸ“‹ Final, polished event plan is displayed in the UI.  

